Advanced properties for preferred, alternative, and hidden labels from established labeling vocabularies.
-
•
Properties intended for textual definitions, notes, and scope descriptions.
-
•
Commonly used properties for synonyms and textual definitions found in scientific and biomedical domains.
-
•
Any custom property explicitly defined as an owl:AnnotationProperty within the ontology itself.
